attributes.title: Seconds to Showtime
attributes.caption: Getting ready for a big show absolutely involves dropping a kickball into some mashed potatoes.
attributes.description: Achievement Hunter and Funhaus have made it to Newark and are ready for the first show of the Let's Play Live tour. Come along as they learn some bus etiquette and get ready for their first big show.
attributes.show_title: Let's Play Live: Life on Tour

attributes.title: The Bus is Lava
attributes.caption: Who doesn't love a bus full of farts?
attributes.description: On this edition of Achievement Hunter and Funhaus Cribz, the crew get acquainted with their tiny bus rooms, play a little floor is lava, and deal with a deadly gas.
attributes.show_title: Let's Play Live: Life on Tour

attributes.title: Kickball Keepy-Uppies
attributes.caption: Keep the ball in the air and please don't break anything.
attributes.description: With 25 minutes until showtime, Achievement Hunter and Funhaus should be getting ready for the show. The key word here being should. Instead, the boys are busy playing their favorite sport. If you're from the Funhaus side of the globe, you'll know this game as Kickball Hacky Sack. But if you live in the Achievement Hunter hemisphere, you'll know this game better as Keepy-Uppies.
attributes.show_title: Let's Play Live: Life on Tour

attributes.title: Midnight McDonald's
attributes.caption: Jack needs his Macca's!
attributes.description: After a show, Achievement Hunter and Funhaus need a midnight snack. McDonald's is open...but only through the drive through. No way is the tour bus fitting through there!
attributes.show_title: Let's Play Live: Life on Tour

attributes.title: The Complete Mall Experience
attributes.caption: There's no  better way to say "Happy Let's Play Live" than with a cookie cake.
attributes.description: Between shows, Funhaus has a day to kill in South Carolina. Their choices were hang out at the local church or go to the mall. They decided to go with the one that sells cookie cakes.
attributes.show_title: Let's Play Live: Life on Tour

attributes.title: Sauce Drinkers Part 1 - Elyse’s Garlic Sauce
attributes.caption: Drink the sauce. Get da money.
attributes.description: Elyse really fuckin' loves Papa John's garlic sauce. Everyone else on the bus chips in some cash to see just how much garlic love there really is.
attributes.display_title: S1:E6 - Sauce Drinkers Part 1 - Elyse’s Garlic Sauce
attributes.show_title: Let's Play Live: Life on Tour

attributes.title: Sauce Drinkers Part 2 - Michael’s Three-In-One Special
attributes.caption: Drink the suace. Get da money...again!
attributes.description: Michael, Gavin, Ryan, and Michael's brother got some food and a few too many drinks. Before getting kicked out of the bar, Gavin sets a bounty for drinking all the sauces that came with Ryan's dinner - ketchup, tiger sauce, and fancy gravy.
attributes.display_title: S1:E7 - Sauce Drinkers Part 2 - Michael’s Three-In-One Special
attributes.show_title: Let's Play Live: Life on Tour
